{"tid":640591,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[恭喜你] 黎明回應得女：感恩醫務人員照顧 望媒體給予空間","createTime":"2018-04-24T11:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T20:42:35.000Z","uid":82917,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"85f90f546a9b7e339d9c24e53ad41f2a0a08cf58","tid":640591,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"51歲黎明，昨天升級當爸！助手阿Wing早產一個月生下女兒。4月24日下午，黎明在個人社交平台發文回應：「用我真摯感恩謝謝醫院的接生護士們和醫生們，他們的專業令我100%尊敬，但最終都是由不知名的人士報料給記者而又令到該醫院變成記者守候的場地！又不知會帶來多少壓力給其他醫務人員和其她產婦與病人，也會因我而影響了其她產婦的休息和打擾了要看病的人士，早產嬰兒的父母是要專注和醫生配合，但如果我再次出現也會令醫院增添多一層的壓力。辛苦了收了上級指令在等候的記者們！我也望各新聞媒體上級可收回攝記守候指令，等醫院可恢復正常，因為我不會再出現醫院，寧願選擇在有私人空間的場合享受與家人在一起。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/192025_a425c659d04137aab68c06368dfbdc7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F192025_a425c659d04137aab68c06368dfbdc7e.png&h=ff4fea4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大美人我係到<br />\n恭喜黎天王<br />\n一索得女！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  恭喜恭喜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/192206_7828b16f768252f57ba1e40d8ebfb168.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F192206_7828b16f768252f57ba1e40d8ebfb168.png&h=fd2a78fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d31e0716b482adeb10eba9bdc847cdebbd715dc6","tid":640591,"uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"助手離婚揀黎明<br />\n<br />\nIn Wong jer we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2292c4c02e9697300f097dc784514b57ddc9db2","tid":640591,"uid":176935,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:26:16.000Z","msg":"黎天王講野真係好得睇<img s